{"name": "orcestra", "metadata": {"name": "orcestra", "version": "0.0.27", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13"], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["aiohttp", "astropy", "cartopy", "cmocean", "easygems", "flox", "fsspec", "geopandas", "gpxpy", "healpix", "intake", "intake-xarray", "ipfsspec", "ipywidgets", "matplotlib", "numpy", "pandas", "pyproj", "requests", "scipy", "seaborn", "sgp4", "simplekml", "textalloc", "topojson", "xarray", "zarr"], "summary": "Tools around the ORCESTRA field campaign", "upload_time": 1733331633}, "documentation": ["# Python tools for ORCESTRA campaign\n\n## install\n\nThe latest released version can be installed using:\n\n```\npip install orcestra\n```\n\n## developing\n\nThis project uses [ruff](https://github.com/astral-sh/ruff) for code formatting and [pre-commit](https://pre-commit.com/) to run the formatter automatically.\n\nPlease ensure that you have `pre-commit` configured locally by running:\n\n```\npre-commit install\n```\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "orcestra.meteor", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "orcestra.meteor.get_meteor_track", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "deduplicate_latlon", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Load the METEOR track from DShip data and return as xr.Dataset.\n\nArgs:\n  deduplicate_latlon (bool): Deprecated."]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "orcestra.tools", "documentation": ["!/usr/bin/env python3"], "functions": [{"name": "orcestra.tools.mpl2rgba", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "mpl", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "orcestra.tools._cmap2windy_rgba", 